Love Island - Series 3, Episode 7




Week two begins and there is no let-up in pace as the games and surprises continue. Romance is on the cards and nobody wants to leave, especially when there is 50,000 pounds up for grabs for the winning couple, but somebody's dreams will be shattered before long as lust gives way to mistrust.
